Name: Turtle Roll
Description: The eggs with that rice and seasoning were lovely.

DescriptionLocalization.es: Los huevos con ese arroz y condimentos eran encantadores.
DescriptionLocalization.ko: 그 밥과 조미료를 곁들인 계란은 사랑 스러웠습니다.
DescriptionLocalization.de: Die Eier mit Reis und Gewürzen waren herrlich.
DescriptionLocalization.fr: Les œufs avec ce riz et cet assaisonnement étaient délicieux.
DescriptionLocalization.hu: A tojás a rizzsel és a fűszerezéssel kedves volt.
DescriptionLocalization.it: Le uova con quel riso e condimento erano deliziose.
DescriptionLocalization.ja: あのご飯と調味料の入った卵が素敵でした。
DescriptionLocalization.pt: Os ovos com esse arroz e tempero ficou adorável.
DescriptionLocalization.ru: Яйца с этим рисом и приправой были прекрасны.
DescriptionLocalization.tr: O pilav ve baharatla birlikte yumurtalar çok güzeldi.
DescriptionLocalization.zh: 那个米饭和调味料的鸡蛋很可爱。
